title: The Country That I Love - An Exile's Memories (1925) [PDF]
description:
THE COUNTRY THAT I LOVE
An Exile's Memories 
by Marie Queen of Rumania
Illustrated by Queen Elizabeth of Greece
Duckworth, London, 1925

For my best friend online; a true daughter of the beautiful Romanian countryside. She is every bit as lovely to match; in mind, body and spirit. I am honored to know her. :)

This charming, simple and short memoir plays out like a love letter to Romania; written by a Queen and illustrated by another. It is a wistful look at the wonderful country and all that it has to offer.

This torrent contains the original PDF, as well as the front cover of the original publication and the gorgeous frontispiece by Queen Elizabeth. Please seed, and enjoy!
